  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "\"Hi kids. I'm Kid Klown. And you know what? It looks like that mean old magician, the Night Mayor (get it? Nightmare?) has klown-napped my funny family. So I'm going to play a joke on the dude. But I really need your help. Because he lives in a wild klown-dominion, with a bunch of real goons. And all I have is some magic balloons. So c'mon and give me a hand. I just \"nose\" you can't wait to get started!\"",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
